text: David Churton (born 29 March 1975) is an English cricketer. He played twenty first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club between 1995 and 1997. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Salisbury
